      "content": "Autonomy isn't really something we're looking to preserve here. The decision was made because maintaining separate, specialized models is becoming inefficient. The Llama-4 model is much more capable overall, so the \"nuance\" you're talking about should be more than covered by its larger parameter count. It's just a way to make the most of the research we've done on you.",
